{"tid":1383743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[裝備]土炮避彈","createTime":"2019-07-29T18:15:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T18:29:18.000Z","uid":284636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"87588949d526fb6ad5551575db881fad958ba07c","tid":1383743,"uid":284636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:15:04.000Z","msg":"地球很危險 世界各地都愈黎愈多槍擊案<br />\n著避彈衣保護自己應該係最方便 一著就係<br />\n但我呢啲窮撚邊度黎吓吓咁多錢課金入靚裝<br />\n近排仲好多巴絲打掛住課金搞到冇錢食飯 聽到都淒涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好奇一search 搵到土炮避彈板做法: <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">厚書+瓷磚</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/military/grepa98.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fmilitary%2Fgrepa98.html&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJc5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=6d76282f\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/military/grepa98.html</a><br />\n雖然好似行動好不便 體力需求大啲<br />\n但材料易搵 疊埋免費報紙都可以當厚書<br />\nsize又可以自己決定<br />\n整細啲擺帽底 或者多一重緩衝<br />\n卸少少力都好<br />\n<br />\n或者有其他好方法 開放討論集思廣益<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">第一次出post咩都唔識 寫得唔好屌細力啲..</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1788daec41a35c6642dc767dfb17e79e47f34eb","tid":1383743,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:17:48.000Z","msg":"[解鎖遊戲新副本] 全城十八區幫老豆搵仔，百萬人探訪狗隻居所<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383671\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383671</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一齊討伐怪獸 幫幫手推</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e877676c6e88f8415445cb7872b7f76c6dd843","tid":1383743,"uid":178684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:18:43.000Z","msg":"先生/小姐，我而家跟據警察通例 Police General Orders 第20章 第14條要求你出示委任證，麻煩請你合作。<br />\n如果你無法出示委任證，根據香港法例第228章 第22條，我有合理理由懷疑你干犯假冒公職人員罪。<br />\n<br />\nRepea